{"tid":1985392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打試過下面流足幾星期啡","createTime":"2020-04-23T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T10:22:03.000Z","uid":61288,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a713199e8fdb9b9804214003d37c452b6936a365","tid":1985392,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"我經期一向唔準同亂，最近五年會間中流啡，不過最近呢兩年唔知係咪工作壓力大，一開始流一兩個星期會自動停<br />\n到最近呢兩年每半年就會有一次流足幾個星期都未完，<br />\n<br />\n2018年同2019年尾都因為黎得太長，個陣照過超聲波，冇任何異樣，醫生話係內分泌失調，食左黃體銅就冇事，之後黎正常m，最近呢個月又黎啡，睇左次中醫，食左幾次藥 係少左好多，但開始黎d帶少少淺啡既白帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊睇西醫好唔好 但我唔想又食黃體銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定睇多次中醫好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉d m咁樣 將來點生仔 好驚自己不育 因為好想同依家個男有將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打有類似經驗 真係覺得好煩同驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 冇搞過野"},{"pid":"a5d1ba3aa2eaef15c5f09478fd6ea379e23c5215","tid":1985392,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"幾大<br />\n有冇拎野去化驗<br />\n有冇痛有冇異感<br />\n<br />\nbtw睇診所唔掂就去醫院"},{"pid":"c81dda2c5c29775c860b8835a75baaa74a2313f1","tid":1985392,"uid":152092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}